{"tid":1199074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★None care送終？】新居屋已超額認購39倍！","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T14:51:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2861bf5f978663a80b1368cee26155a9b5afa8d8","tid":1199074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"房委會推出、共提供4800多個單位的新一期居屋，認購反應熱烈。截至今日(10日)下午5時，樂富房委會客務中心累計收到約51,000份以文本形式遞交的「居屋2019」和「白居二2019」申請表。至於今次新增的網上申請，房委會累計收到約144,000份「居屋2019」和 72,000份「白居二2019」申請。意味將於周三（12日）晚上7時截止的新居屋申請，至今已至少超額認購39倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190610/bkn-20190610191236196-0610_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190610%2Fbkn-20190610191236196-0610_00822_001.html&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=ed472ef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190610/bkn-20190610191236196-0610_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a68954f1ec286add02fa0e3d8065f2909ded52a1","tid":1199074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c427fac0c82261808492e63db2fbd5871651f122","tid":1199074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SvLyiiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSvLyiiS.jpg&h=a25883a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1209537ef261e28fe4a415bbda245cf473b79f8","tid":1199074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"464529f417977d569df133ff47098d41cb2f02dc","tid":1199074,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c427fac0c82261808492e63db2fbd5871651f122","tid":1199074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:38:07.000Z",